sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Webhook as Operator Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Operator as Operator Controller<br/>controller-runtime
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Data Science Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant MR as model-registry REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Model Registry Instance Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply ModelRegistry CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-...<br/>HTTPS/9443, API server cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Defaulted CR<br/>(Istio→OAuth→KubeRBACProxy migration)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-...<br/>HTTPS/9443, API server cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission allowed
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created

    Note over Operator,DB: Reconciliation Loop
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event: ModelRegistry
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>(model-registry + kube-rbac-proxy)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Service (8443/TCP)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Route ({name}-https)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute<br/>(in HTTPROUTE_NAMESPACE)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ReferenceGrant<br/>(cross-namespace)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Group ({name}-users)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Role + RoleBinding
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>(auth-delegator)

    Note over User,DB: Flow 2: Client → Model Registry via Route

    User->>Route: GET /api/model_registry/...<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    Route->>KRBAC: TLS Passthrough<br/>HTTPS/8443
    KRBAC->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>KRBAC: Token valid
    KRBAC->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>KRBAC: Access granted
    KRBAC->>MR: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080 (localhost)
    MR->>DB: Query metadata<br/>5432/TCP, Password auth
    DB-->>MR: Result set
    MR-->>KRBAC: JSON response
    KRBAC-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>User: JSON response

    Note over User,DB: Flow 3: Client → Model Registry via Gateway API

    User->>Gateway: GET /model-registry/{name}/...<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBAC: HTTPRoute match<br/>URLRewrite strips prefix<br/>HTTPS/8443
    KRBAC->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SAR
    K8sAPI-->>KRBAC: Authorized
    KRBAC->>MR: HTTP/8080 (localhost)
    MR->>DB: Query<br/>SSL configurable
    DB-->>MR: Result
    MR-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS response
    Gateway-->>User: JSON response
